      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Create a new Node\n- if index === 0, use addAtHead method\n- if index === size of list, use addAtTail method\n- traverse to the position \n  - start from head and move to the index position\n  - update new nodes next to current nodes next\n  - update current nodes next to the new node\n  - increase the size of the list\n",
      "fontSize": 74.39982096354359,
