      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Formula execution engine: Implement a\nformula parser and evaluator in the\nCellEditor component to handle user-entered\nformulas, allowing for dynamic calculations\nand updates to cell values.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Formula execution engine: Implement a formula parser and evaluator in the CellEditor component to handle user-entered formulas, allowing for dynamic calculations and updates to cell values.",
